Print GitHub Markdown in Single Click.

Discover the ultimate solution for effortlessly printing GitHub Flavored Markdown with just a single click. Our extension empowers you to accurately reproduce the visual appeal of GitHub's Markdown rendering, delivering professional-grade printouts without any hassle.
Why struggle with convoluted methods like downloading markdown files and running them through converters? Our streamlined process ensures you can print GitHub Markdown with unmatched speed and ease, saving you precious time and effort.

Whether you're navigating GitHub repositories, wikis, or issues, our extension seamlessly integrates into your workflow, providing a convenient printing experience for all your Markdown content.

Enjoy the convenience of two-click printing on any page within the GitHub universe, including both GitHub and GitHub Enterprise. Whether you're printing documentation, code snippets, or project notes, our extension guarantees consistency and fidelity in the printed output.
Embrace a new era of effortless Markdown printing with our extension. Enhance your productivity and make your GitHub content come to life in print, exactly as you see it on screen. Try it now and experience GitHub Flavored Markdown printing like never before.
